notes.body: Hello Manohar,     Greetings from PharmEasy!  With regards to your order #657351323376488448-32482, the estimated delivery date is 11th December 2025.  I would like to inform you that the estimated date of delivery depends on the availability of the medicines and the delivery pin code. Also, be informed, PharmEasy will always try to ensure that your order is delivered at the earliest as we completely understand the urgency of the medicine.  As of now, the speed-up delivery feature is unavailable with us. Once the order is out for delivery, you will receive an SMS with the contact details of the delivery executive along with the 4-digit pin. Once the details are shared with you, you may coordinate with the delivery executive for exact timings.     For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the 'Need Help' section.  Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.       Regards,  Devdas.
notes.body_html:
Hello Manohar,

Greetings from PharmEasy!

With regards to your order #657351323376488448-32482, the estimated delivery date is 11th December 2025.

I would like to inform you that the estimated date of delivery depends on the availability of the medicines and the delivery pin code. Also, be informed, PharmEasy will always try to ensure that your order is delivered at the earliest as we completely understand the urgency of the medicine.

As of now, the speed-up delivery feature is unavailable with us. Once the order is out for delivery, you will receive an SMS with the contact details of the delivery executive along with the 4-digit pin. Once the details are shared with you, you may coordinate with the delivery executive for exact timings.

For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the 'Need Help' section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.

Regards,
Devdas.
